{
  "page": "Tourney at Old Oak",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <b>tourney at Old Oak</b> was held in the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_73_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">73&#160;AC</a> during the reign of <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Old_Oak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> was held at <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Oak\" title=\"Old Oak\">Old Oak</a> by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\">Oakheart</a>, who was celebrating the birth of a young son with seven days of jousting. A <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a> known as the Silver Fool took part in the tourney, accounting himself well before falling to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Redwyne\" title=\"Rickard Redwyne\">Rickard Redwyne</a>. Rickard helped the mystery knight to his feet and unmasked him, revealing the Silver Fool to be none other than Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a>. Rickard bade Baelon to kneel, and knighted the prince on the spot. A feast was held after the conclusion of the jousting to make the tourney's end.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_long_reign_-_jaehaerys_and_alysanne:_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Joust\">The Joust</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_at_Old_Oak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Joust\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rowan\" title=\"House Rowan\"><img alt=\"House Rowan.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Rowan.svg/32px-House_Rowan.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Rowan.svg/48px-House_Rowan.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Rowan.svg/64px-House_Rowan.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a> defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rowan\" title=\"House Rowan\">Rowan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall\" title=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall\"><img alt=\"House Fossoway of Cider Hall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/32px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/48px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/aa/House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg/64px-House_Fossoway_of_Cider_Hall.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a> defeated both <a href=\"/index.php/Fossoway_twins\" title=\"Fossoway twins\">Fossoway twins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/48px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/64px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Ashford\" title=\"House Ashford\"><img alt=\"House Ashford.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/House_Ashford.svg/32px-House_Ashford.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/House_Ashford.svg/48px-House_Ashford.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/House_Ashford.svg/64px-House_Ashford.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Baelon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Baelon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Baelon Targaryen</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Ashford\" title=\"Alyn Ashford\">Alyn Ashford</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/32px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/i